bonfyre-repurpose — turn brief artifacts into social media formats

Usage:
  bonfyre-repurpose <format> <brief-dir> <output-dir>

Formats:
  tweet-thread   Twitter/X thread (5-7 tweets)
  linkedin       LinkedIn post (hook → insight → CTA)
  carousel       Instagram/LinkedIn carousel slides
  youtube-desc   YouTube description + chapters + SEO
  newsletter     Email newsletter edition
  all            Generate all formats

Example:
  bonfyre-repurpose all ./output/brief ./output/social
